- Build and test on device with Dolby Atmos enabled — verify spatial audio gracefully degrades (EQ-only, no artifacts).
- Cold launch app — verify no card closing animation on startup.
- Toggle cards open/close, kill app, relaunch — verify state persists.
- Play music across genres — verify zero-centered EQ sounds clean with no muddiness.
